description: The web app provides multiple game for prediction such as: BO, Market,… In which, user can predict price in future or win/loss between two entities. All of the transaction is transparency becaused of implemented through the blockchain mechanism.

1988Dragon sells gift cards that users can use as vouchers to buy clothing, electronics, groceries,... – even accommodations and flights for their next vacation. These gift cards are not physical but vouchers users receive via e-wallet, which they can redeem when paying later for products at partnered merchants

AI Care Pro is one of the first fitness brands to enter the hugely exciting Blockchain-NFT market and launch a range of NFTs. Partnering with Getfit, a chain of Gym and Yoga centers, the AI Care Pro project will deliver advanced user experiences through a fitness D-app and provide a limited-edition range of NFTs.
